Cadbury's Gems are not just liked by kids but even grown-ups, reasons to which are many. Try the new crunchy, colourful and chocolatey Kwality Walls Cadbury Gems Burst This ice cream give you the pop in your mouth that melts slowly, giving you an irresistible feeling.

About the Brand: Wall’s, has been making ice cream for almost 100 years and are sold in over 50 different countries around the world. Today they go by all sorts of different names in each one.
